title: David Cameron rejects plans for another EU referendum if public votes to leave
text: David Cameron has slapped down the plan favoured by Boris Johnson , one of the leading candidates to succeed him as Tory leader, for a second EU referendum in the event of the first one resulting in a vote to leave. A senior Cameron aide
